caption: Idk what all these 1 star reviews is about. I ordered 2 bowls STUFFED PACKED a steak burrito SIZE OF A NEWBORN BABY.  I live a mile away and my delivery got to me in 20 minutes.

Horrible experience. I waited 30 min for an online order. I ordered 2 burrito bowls and the employees had no record of the transaction. After complaining to the cashier for the second time she had someone prepare my food. My bag seemed light so I looked inside and there were 2 burritos inside. I went back and told the cashier and she apologized about the mistake and said she would correct it. I got a bag with food Inside and rushed away. When I got home I found they put both BURRITOS in bowls. Are you kidding me? This was a deliberate act. To top it off they didn't have any meat in them and we're half the size of a normal burrito. I will never return. Stay away from this place at all costs!

It’s sad that it’s 6:45pm and there’s no chicken, no cauliflower rice.  We waited more than 15 minutes and still no food.  The servers were polite but could not give a time as to when the food would be ready.

I hardly write a bad review but this place gives you little to no food. I spent $26 on a chicken bowl and I had little to zero chicken. Please believe the reviews about this place. Never shall I order from that location again. I still love Chipotle but this place is a disappointment. All that money only to received very little food....smdh!!! The owner needs to really supervise these worker and see how the costumers are getting cheated.
First time trying chipotle and I will never go back. I paid 25.00 for two bowls of nothing. Portion size for kids. It was ridiculous!

Isn't it interesting how over 50 negative 1 Star reviews including my own....magically disappeared.  This place is the pits.  They raised prices over $2 for each item after the opening week.  Drive Thru/ Mobile ordering is always down.  Portions are tiny.  Outside of NYC Chipotle is always a fine option but just like every other Chipotle in the area, it is terrible. Check reviews none of them exceed 2 Stars.
